hat you keep working even harder despite having more money than you could e=
ver need. And then there are a few modern big tech companies that are sort =
of an exception to the exception, where it=C2=A0<em>is=C2=A0</em>common to =
get rich, keep your job, but not really do much work anymore: Alphabet and =
Meta have recreated the leisure class. And then the exception to the except=
